OL,4,CVatican tightens rules on supernatural
OL,5,Cphenomena
OL,6,GWhen are reports of a weeping statue
OL,7,Gfake news? How credible is the claim
OL,8,Gthat a holy relic led to a miraculous
OL,9,Ghealing? And how should a divine
OL,10,Gapparition be confirmed?
OL,12,FThese are the themes addressed in the
OL,13,FVatican's new guidelines on
OL,14,Fsupernatural phenomena, which urge the
OL,15,FCatholic church to take a more
OL,16,Fcautious approach.
OL,18,FThe document, compiled by the
OL,19,FVatican's Dicastery for the Doctrine
OL,20,Fof the Faith, lays out stricter rules
OL,21,Fto assess the truthfulness of such
OL,22,Fclaims.
